Posts.Content: Be careful, I've read lots of stories here and other forums where the initial dose was too high and an embarrassing trip to the emergency room was necessary. I started at around .03 I think, and that was good. I tried to use one of the automatic injectors but found it too difficult to control. I used it for around a year until normal erections returned.
